description: And he gave a super sweet shoutout to the Chicago Mahomies!
maintext:
Chicago Mahomie’s were losing their minds when we were about to interview Austin Mahone backstage during the pre-Grammy interviews.
When he finally stopped by our station, he gave both Chicago Mahomie’s and B96 a super sweet shoutout.
He also dished about his upcoming new music and if he prefers Chicago pizza or Chicago girls. (We think you’ll like his answer!)
Watch in the player above!
title: Austin Mahone Picks Between Chicago Pizza & Chicago Girls During Pre-GRAMMY Interviews
